item.title: FAST: A College Basketball Metric
item.description: FAST is a one-number metric to help inform of the next two-way1NBA stars. FAST stands for: Free throws Age Steals Turnovers Player Name FAST Score Jabari Smith 100 Paolo Banchero 99 1- Weighted combined offensive and defensive impact. E.g., FAST likes Chris Paul more than Trae Young.
